data.description: ***MOTIVATED SELLER*** Come home to Marion Oaks, conveniently located among local golf courses, walking and biking trails and just under 1 mile to I-75. NO HOA fees. When you pull up to this beautiful home, you will enter through an inviting front porch sitting area. Enjoy privacy, while mature trees divide your property from your only side neighbor. This split floor plan 3/2/2 is warm and welcoming and gives you an eat in NEW kitchen, with open views to dining and family room. Inside laundry and storage. Lots of closet space in this house! The Master bedroom is made for your king size bed and has a walk-in closet. The master bath has a Roman style soaking tub, separate commode room and stand up shower. The NEWLY ADDED FRENCH DOORS in the living room open to a fenced-in backyard where special moments will take place, grilling or just relaxing with friends and family and your small or big pets. Within Marion Oaks you will find recreation/fitness center, park with playground, library, shuffle board, basketball courts and Sheriffs Office only within 1/2 mile distance from home. Schedule your private showing before it's gone!!! Stop looking and make this YOUR home!!!
